<br>
I don't want to jump the gun here, but I think I see a few factions that might coalesce around specific petitions.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Minor Fixes Only:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> A collection of minor fixes.  Does not conflict with other petitions<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Increase Pet Power Through Mixed Means:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Reasonable, but seems to become harder to do in light of the damage figures we are collecting.  Given pathing difficulties and risk, may not solve problem.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Remove Pet Penalties:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Pets are not worth the penalties we incurr, so eliminate or reduce these.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Indifferent Pets:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Leave pet power as it, but dramaticly reduce the risk of pets on raids or near bad pathing.  Conflicts with <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Increase Pet Power</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> and <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Remove Pet Penalties</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> above.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Better Nukes:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Forget pets, get me more power, <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Scotty</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  Conflicts with most pet petitions.<br>
<br>
If I had to pick likely winners, I would suggest that either <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Pet Power</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> or <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Indifferent Pets</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> would garner the most support from <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Magicians</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  These are in conflict with each other, however, and <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Indifferent Pets</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> is a radical proposal.<br>
<br>
However, we are still a long way from being able to argue <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Indifferent Pets</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> successfully.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Razamatazz Pizzazz</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
